				\begin{document}$$10^\mathrm{5}$$\end{document} samples, 105\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$10^\mathrm{5}$$\end{document} samples were excluded from the regression-based learning process for testing and validation purpose.Fig. 10
Coefficients of polynomial chaos series representation using least angle regression (LAR) for RTC France (57 mm) solar cellFig. 11
Coefficients of polynomial chaos series representation using least angle regression (LAR) for Solarex MSX83 solar cell

